43 of a less than maximum federal Pell Grant; and
44 (7) students admitted to the institution through regular decision, with separate
45 disaggregated reporting within by major racial subgroup, receipt of a maximum federal Pell
46 Grant and receipt of a less than maximum federal Pell Grant;
47 (iii) the number of student applicants identified as having legacy status and their
48 admission rate, as well as the percentage of admitted legacy students among all admitted
49 students, and their enrollment rate;
50 (iv) the number of student applicants who apply early decision and early action,
51 and admission rate of each; and
